    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="transcript" id="J244">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>It is easy to work when the soul is at play --</l>
                    <l>But when the soul is in pain --</l>
                    <l>The hearing him put his playthings up</l>
                    <l>Makes work difficult -- then --</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>It is simple, to ache in the Bone, or the Rind</l>
                    <l>But Gimblets -- among the nerve --</l>
                    <l>Mangle daintier -- terribler --</l>
                    <l>Like a Panther in the Glove --</l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
